headline.main: U.S. BELIEVED TOPIC; Brenner Meeting Seen Laying Plans to Offset Our Expected Entry ATLANTIC IS ONE PROBLEM Nazis Stress Military Aspect of Parley -- Mediterranean Drive Forecast in Rome AXIS CHIEFS CHART WAR STEPS IN TALK

lead_paragraph: ROME, June 2 -- With the Axis forces in possession of Crete, Reichsfuehrer Hitler and Premier Mussolini met today at the Brenner Pass for five hours to decide upon their next military and political moves.
